 video ad for the Squatty Potty, which appeared on Shark Tank. As of this recording, the video has 43 million combined video views from Facebook, YouTube and some freebooted video.</p> <p>httpv://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbYWhdLO43Q</p> <p>Although Derral found that Facebook video is good for branding and engagement, he says the video got better conversions with YouTube.</p> <p>Listen to the show to discover the benefit of Facebook video versus YouTube.</p> <p>The process for making video ads</p> <p>Derral says you need to start by determining what you want to accomplish with your video ad. He cautions that if you have 80, 10 or even 3 things you want to accomplish, then it's never going to work. You need narrow it down to one reason to make the ad. Then everything else will benefit from it.</p> Do you post videos on YouTube? Want to know what makes a video ad successful? To discover how YouTube video ads work, I interview Derral Eves. More About This Show The Social Media Marketing podcast is an on-demand talk radio show from Social Media Exa... clean 53:08 Blogging Tools: Apps to Better Manage Your Blog http://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/tools-apps-to-better-manage-your-blog-ian-cleary/ Fri, 13 Nov 2015 11:00:26 +0000 http://dev-socialmediaexaminer.pantheon.io/?p=92029 <img width="150" height="78" src="http://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ms-podcast171-iancleary-560-150x78.png" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="ms-podcast171-iancleary-560" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; clear:both;" srcset="http://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ms-podcast171-iancleary-560-150x78.png 150w, http://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ms-podcast171-iancleary-560.png 560w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /><p>Do you have a blog?</p> <p>Want to improve the content development, publishing and promotion processes?</p> <p>To discover how to streamline your blogging with the b